---
title: Quick Caribbean Beef & Pork Rissoles with Charred Corn Slaw & Avocado
description: Charred corn is the perfect addition to a colourful slaw, it's juicy and sweet. Keep tastiness going by spicing the beef
and pork rissoles in a Caribbean jerk seasoning. It’s a dish that leaves a pleasant, warm feeling after you're done.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

